Keep Solaris GLib tests from masking regressions when the platform support is
available through Solaris-specific packaging or modules.

Also skip the g_usleep(0) versus g_usleep(1) timing comparison on Solaris i386;
it is probabilistic and unreliable under loaded BOB builders.

--- a/glib/meson.build
+++ b/glib/meson.build
